  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nHow to update the ETH1_BLOCK_HASH value in vars.env according to the genesis.json in the Start the local testnet?\r\n\r\n## Version\r\n\r\nLighthouse v4.4.1-2841f60 cargo 1.72.1 (103a7ff2e 2023-08-15)\r\n\r\n## Present Behaviour\r\n\r\nwhen I modify the genesis.json and then start the local testnet, the chain is not working beacuse of the wrong ETH1_BLOCK_HASH, so I want to modify this hash value, but i do not know how.\r\n\r\n\r\n",
