    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "After you modified `genesis.json`, you can obtained the updated `ETH1_BLOCK_HASH` with `geth init genesis.json`, which will generate a new genesis state that you can enquire with `\r\neth.getBlock('latest')`. From there you get the hash, and update it in `vars.env`.\r\n\r\nHope this helps\r\n",
